"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"People can have ownership of an NFT, but they can’t use it for commercial purpose. The reason why people buy NFT is that they have a belief in scarcity.\\n\\nThen my art work could be licensed for free in the future. People can use the image for free, but they have to pay if they want to actually own the image. However if people use it for commercial purposes to make a profit, they cannot be free.\\n\\nA new smart contract standard can be created for this. If the original NFT works is copied, such as printing or derivative products, then a new NFT will be generated on the basis of this NFT. The original NFT is the parent NFT, and the newly generated NFT is the child NFT. Then we can set a royalty fee, every time a child NFT is sold, the original author can get a certain cut. For example, I can set the royalty fee to 5%. Consumers can check the NFT to determine whether they have bought an authorized product. In this way, an NFT is bound to a real object. A programmable NFT contract may be required so that every time an automatic authorization is issued, one or more tokens can be automatically generated for each authorization.\",\"timestamp\":1641119572,\"title\":\"Capsule（16.4.2021）Copyright is absurd, and its essence is hegemony.\"},\"digest\":\"9WmOQ8nn2wIVSnbmPyh7S_JT7z1oXgr3ZBatrB7yY2I\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE828f8bE1a3CB994133936fB4D9A708a7D192462\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"30oV-kOFSC9lQBdHEarttZfxjliQz8okqoKZUNLBj88\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"oE3PBJa5icihwzV4Vo38ifbPXR099aDCDl_ixLAomho\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"OryYvAregangYZ55vRcq10fhCQgi0uzQLIFw-byqu_vHpeNNwGVpseYQ84FL9B3bpSUhQatobx3lrcDTQ3e4Kw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x31cd513577813d56dac188e35743ecb529db0e03e283593e4cc226acb4e7611a5a06f0e8d95703de997b6dc6c43ffc9841842d11590b5c80d29579b563e532581b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"30oV-kOFSC9lQBdHEarttZfxjliQz8okqoKZUNLBj88\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"oE3PBJa5icihwzV4Vo38ifbPXR099aDCDl_ixLAomho\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"9WmOQ8nn2wIVSnbmPyh7S_JT7z1oXgr3ZBatrB7yY2I\"}"